            review: 'Lectures are mostly going thru the slides and very difficult to follow the steps. Legacy software like winbugs does no good to the course. I am not sure how much is useful these are for real data analytics.\nThis has been my toughest class to understand in the 6 classes that I have taken so far.',
            rating: 1,
